{"tid":2120098,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"袁嘉蔚：譚耀宗公然承認種票？","createTime":"2020-07-22T12:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T13:04:55.000Z","uid":105567,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"81bddaee0a0d63e795d15bbaa5b74d100f13b535","tid":2120098,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kawaitiffany/photos/a.981332475352467/1655680707917637/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkawaitiffany%2Fphotos%2Fa.981332475352467%2F1655680707917637%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgIvgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=6f6bf837\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kawaitiffany/photos/a.981332475352467/1655680707917637/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n民建聯切勿知法犯法！<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委、前民建聯主席 #譚耀宗 籍疫情為由，要求政府延遲投票。他指原因是有建制派選民居於大陸，而且在香港沒有住所，在疫情下難以隔離14日再投票。今日他又對傳媒說「選民只要在香港有居住地方，即使不是在香港經常居住，都合資格投票。」」<br />\n<br />\n但事實上，在《立法會條例》當中早已列明，任何人登記做選民時，都必須符合「#通常在香港居住」的規定，而且申報的住址必須是「#在香港唯一或主要的居所」。<br />\n<br />\n前任香港政制及內地事務局局長譚志源亦分別在2012及2014年回覆立法會議員提問，清楚指明「任何人士在選民登記或更改選民住址的申請中作出虛假陳述，即觸犯選舉法例」以及「若選民&hellip;&hellip;已不再符合法例規定的登記資格並因此喪失投票資格，故他應將其最新的資料通知選舉事務處」。<br />\n<br />\n按照政府的官方說法，若然選民已經不在香港經常居住，甚至在香港沒有住所，理應立即通知選舉事務處，取消選民資格。如果他在選民登記作出虛假陳述，更是違反法例！<br />\n<br />\n⚠️譚耀宗公然承認 #種票，是否代表民建聯一向知法犯法？選舉臨近，大家一定要嚴防種票，不要誤墜法網！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3XTkeYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3XTkeYD.jpg&h=d9e0b5aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2590f6a822c0f4d2a6a420185ca121e41185e41","tid":2120098,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"佢係有心定無意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242149c6f26d5caace29a1f2c16c6f3153b6dbc9","tid":2120098,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"鬼拍後尾枕"},{"pid":"0fb8df57f0ab11c3b864f85e2fbe81bd9deb3a25","tid":2120098,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"27781dd1b0ea8da146134232dabafdf023643dc6","tid":2120098,"uid":17209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:59:32.000Z","msg":"有冇其他立法會議員出黎講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果蔚蔚嘅理解係冇錯，咁班狗官真係好廢，香港法治真係已經廢左好耐，耐到令班狗官覺得呢種違法行為已經係常態同正確"},{"pid":"40bab2fb49a12fd99b72aa37078210121d6bcc3f","tid":2120098,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"痰罐中"},{"pid":"180c14c40e41c3b4179a9ad75c552bb6763d8c50","tid":2120098,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:59:45.000Z","msg":"淨係劏房都唔知種左幾多萬票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c0a0b1440c4347e8de348a3334ffa32b9571bc","tid":2120098,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:00:31.000Z","msg":"準備人大釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb55bdb14ae88bf434b77c3823699355b10f20e","tid":2120098,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10df0193339058182df048e06af078ae60bfb0a","tid":2120098,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:04:55.000Z","msg":"條女都係晒澳洲<br />\n<br />\n唔識香港法例都好正常呀"}]}